      "id": "PopularPost115818",
      "post_content": "If you can't make him at least a 5/5, he loses to [Tower Gargoyle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tower Gargoyle) as a 4-drop. I guess it depends how often you'll be wanting to drop him with at least 3 artifacts left in your hand. If your two-drop is some form of acceleration ([Etherium Sculptor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Etherium Sculptor), [Everflowing Chalice](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Everflowing Chalice), etc.), you could conceivably have a 7/7 or so on turn 3, though.",
      "posted_by": "DarthMohawk1",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost115818\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">If you can't make him at least a 5/5, he loses to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Tower Gargoyle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tower Gargoyle\">Tower Gargoyle</a> as a 4-drop. I guess it depends how often you'll be wanting to drop him with at least 3 artifacts left in your hand. If your two-drop is some form of acceleration (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Etherium Sculptor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Etherium Sculptor\">Etherium Sculptor</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Everflowing Chalice\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Everflowing Chalice\">Everflowing Chalice</a>, etc.), you could conceivably have a 7/7 or so on turn 3, though.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '115818'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy21927\">DarthMohawk1</span>\r\n                                (11/14/2010 2:19:55 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_Su